ch.eth.scu.importer.processors.model

Class AbstractDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.eth.scu.importer.processors.model.AbstractDescriptor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DatasetDescriptor, ExperimentDescriptor, FirstLevelDescriptor, LeicaLifProcessor.SubImageDescriptor, RootDescriptor, SampleDescriptor

    public abstract class AbstractDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that represents an entity to be mapped to openBIS. Derived classes of AbstractDescriptor will represent Experiments, Specimens, Trays (Plates), Tubes, Images, SubImages that will be wrapped into the tree viewers and will allow to map the entities to their final location in openBIS. Examples are Experiment, Specimen, Tray, Tube for the BDFACSDIVAXMLProcessor.
    Author:
    Aaron Ponti
